<p>
<lb n="1"/>vīraśrī gajaputi gauḍe
<lb n="2" break="no"/>svara pratāpa kapilesvara
<lb n="3" break="no"/>deva māhārājāṅkara vije
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rāije samasta 33 śrāhi [ka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rkaḍādūti ?] sukala 10 gūru
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vāre jīaradesa deula
<lb n="7"/>Adikāraparikṣāṇe kaude
<lb n="8" break="no"/>sa vehorāṅkara Adhikāre
<lb n="9"/>bhogaparikṣā virudāsa svaji
<lb n="10" break="no"/>āṅkara Adhiṣṭhāṇe śrīnarasi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṅganathadevaṅka lokaḍadā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>sa vehorāṅka Āijñā [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] kāmā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>the bhogaparikṣā virudāsakū
<lb n="14"/>jiā Ebhā Āile cātira
<lb n="15" break="no"/>dinalāgi Apasare pramesa
<lb n="16" break="no"/>raṅkū lāgi hoiva <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> pañcavarnapha
<lb n="17" break="no"/>lacūla śoṇā E 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ethiki va
<lb n="18" break="no"/>rtanabhogaparikṣā vasala bhā
<lb n="19" break="no"/>tamūhā Āṭha 8 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kamāllimākiā
<lb n="20" break="no"/>arnata Ākū māta goṭā 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="21"/>lekā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ee dharma Ācandrāarka
<lb n="22"/>hoithiva [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Ehāje harai se
<lb n="23"/>pramesvaruṅku doroha ho
<lb n="24" break="no"/>i <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī śrī śrī
